<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q32_v8" title="Q32_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Considera la ecuación
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mi>b</m:mi>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      . Se sabe que
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      es solución de esta ecuación. ¿Qué valor debe tener
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>b</m:mi>
      </m:math>
      para que la igualdad sea verdadera?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>-1</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al reemplazar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> en la ecuación, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, luego <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:math> fuera <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, el lado derecho sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y no coincide con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al reemplazar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> en <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, resulta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, o sea <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Al sumar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> en ambos lados, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>-3</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al reemplazar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, el lado izquierdo vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:math> fuera <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, el lado derecho sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-3</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>-5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esa opción no satisface la igualdad.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>-9</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, la ecuación queda <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que el lado izquierdo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:math> fuera <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, el lado derecho sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-9</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>-11</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esa alternativa no hace verdadera la ecuación.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso por sustitución</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Reemplazar el valor de</strong> <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> es solución, se sustituye en la ecuación <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Queda: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Resolver el lado izquierdo</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Y como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, resulta:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Despejar</strong> <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:math></p>
            <p>Sumamos <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> en ambos lados de la igualdad:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>-1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El valor que debe tener <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:math> para que la igualdad sea verdadera es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>